          "title": "Chime SDK Messaging",
          "expandable": true,
          "defaultExpansion": false,
          "helpText": "Messaging is pay-per-use with rates for sending messages, message delivery, and message storage. The Amazon Chime SDK only charges you for what you use, allowing you to scale as needed.",
